title: 11/12/21 DPS Hour 1 Brady Quinn

description:
The guys start the show with the hot topic of Odell Beckham Jr being signed to the Los Angeles Rams. Can OBJ work in a offense where he isn't the #1 target? Brady Quinn joins the show to talk Ravens, OU Football and more!
